-- MOVES-QFC Authority appoints Sheikh Salman Bin Hassan Al-Thani CFO
-- 
-- Mon Jul 14, 2014 10:26AM EDT
-- None



July 14 (Reuters) - Qatar Financial Centre Authority (QFC Authority), the commercial and strategic arm of QFC, said it appointed Sheikh Salman Bin Hassan Al-Thani as chief financial and tax officer.

QFC is a provider of legal and business infrastructure for financial services. QFC Authority said Al-Thani would help it strengthen its business environment for domestic and foreign firms.